data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  Welcome to 3849 Bowfin Trail, a stunning 5-bedroom, 4 1/2-bathroom home in the picturesque Bellalago community, nestled along the serene shoreline of Lake Tohopekaliga. With an abundance of amenities and a perfect blend of luxury and functionality, this home offers the ultimate Florida living experience.  As you approach, you'll be greeted by an inviting front porch, the ideal spot to sip your morning coffee or chat with neighbors. Step inside, and you'll immediately appreciate the open floor plan, designed for modern living. A dedicated home office provides a quiet workspace for productivity. The half bath, discreetly tucked behind the stairs, is a thoughtful addition for guests.  The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, boasting a kitchen island with seating, perfect for food prep and casual dining. A butler's pantry adds convenience and style, making entertaining a breeze.   The kitchen flows seamlessly into the large family room, creating a space that's perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. From the family room, you have easy access to the outdoor lanai, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine and dine al fresco.  The first-floor master suite is a tranquil retreat, featuring ample space and an en-suite bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find a large loft that can serve as a game room or a second family room, offering endless possibilities for relaxation and entertainment.  The upper floor also includes two bedrooms with private en-suites, ensuring comfort and privacy for your family and guests. Two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed full-size bathroom with double sinks and a separate toilet and shower area.  Step outside to the covered screened patio, complete with double fans, and enjoy the Florida sunshine by the sparkling saltwater pool on the paver deck.   This home includes a whole home vacuum system built into the home with plug-in accessories that will give you everything you need to take care of your carpet and tile floors.  Living in Bellalago means access to a wide range of community amenities, including a Basketball Court, Boat Slip, Clubhouse, Dock, Pickleball Court, Playground, Pool, Private Boat Ramp, Recreation Facilities, Security, and Tennis Court. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast or prefer indoor activities, Bellalago has something for everyone.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful Mediterranean-style home your own. Experience the charm and luxury of Bellalago living while being just outside of Orlando. This master-planned community offers lakeside recreation, high-end amenities, and the perfect home for your family.
